title: Total War: WARHAMMER 2 - The Laboratory Gameplay Trailer

json.text: Skaven have been busy, using much warpstone!
What's this-this?? New Laboratory mode in Total War: Warhammer 2!
More units. Yes-Yes. More Skaven, more kill-death, yes-yes!
Ahhhh, Vermintide comes! This is TRUE Skaven army!
Lizard-things so tough and scaly. Crack-‘em like eggs! Die-die!
Tweak-twist some more.
Low gravity. Yes-Yes!
Oooh – floaty elf-things!
Time for pointy-ears to suffer-hurt!
See them fly! Aaaahahaha!
How many doomwheels?! Not enough Doomwheels.
NEVER ENOUGH DOOMWHEELS! Ha-Haaa!
NO MERCY!
Hell-pit beast is best, yes-yes. Make it bigger! Massive-bigger, SQUISH THEM ALL!
Many warp-lightning cannons. Kill-zap! KIIILL-ZAAAAAAP!!
Mess with these things, yeeees. Mess with all the things! *snickers*
Clan Skryre has powerful warp-tech!
Make things bigger, faster, killier, YES!
More-more!
Flick all switches! Pull all levers! Make it break-bust, yes-yes!
